    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term referring to various green stones or minerals, particularly those used as gem stones, such as emerald, or those used as pigment, such as green earth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
